        "TileImage": "$($repository f4b6599a-cef2-494c-87cd-9d0656f34d48).Image",
        "Description": "So, you think you&apos;re hot stuff, do you?\r\rAny idiot can show up with a Sniper Rifle and pick off their target from half a mile away. Where&apos;s the risk? Where&apos;s the creativity? Where&apos;s the excitement?\r\rYou&apos;re going to use that rifle of yours to take out GAMA&apos;s resident Yoga Instructor.\r\rBut don&apos;t think you can just take him out from afar. You&apos;ll need to get up close and personal if you want to pull off a clean hit.\r\rJust be careful that the heat from those hot springs doesn&apos;t fog up your scope.",
